posts.message:
Hello everyone
There are a lot of posts about VPN and SSH in Egypt recently.

Can I ask you please to refrain from making general comments on these posts, and only comment if you have some status update to add (something working, something not working, asking about specific detail in previous update, etc), or providing solutions / workarounds?

This way finding useful information on these posts will be much easier
